Litter, a simple dark mode terminal for GNOME based on Vte. 

  Shortcut          Alt. shortcut     Action
  ===========================================================================
  CTRL TAB                            Switch to next terminal tab
  CTRL SHIFT TAB                      Switch to previous terminal tab

  CTRL SHIFT t                        Open a new terminal tab

  CTRL +            CTRL =            Scale font up
  CTRL -                              Scale font down
  CTRL 0                              Reset font scale

  CTRL SHIFT v                        Clipboard: paste into terminal
  CTRL SHIFT c                        Clipboard: copy selection from terminal
  ===========================================================================

